data.description: Welcome to 115 Kingsbury Court. This traditional 2 story located on a beautiful cul-de-sac, spectacular outdoor space with inground pool. Living room and family room with gas fireplace. Kitchen appliances, granite countertops, 4 season sun room. Partially finished basement plus work shop area. Replacement windows and exterior doors 2015, whole house generator and gas grill hard plumbed
